EmotionSense is an AI-driven facial expression recognition system that predicts human emotions from images. When a user uploads a photo, the model detects the face and classifies expressions such as Happy, Sad, Angry, Neutral, Surprise, Fear, and Disgust.
This project combines Computer Vision and Deep Learning techniques to analyze facial features and deliver accurate emotion predictions.


